A fuller delivery on middle. Rassie van der Dussen works it towards the leg side.
Pulls his length back a little this time, on off. Rassie van der Dussen blocks it towards mid on now.
Goes fuller on off. Rassie van der Dussen drives it to mid off.
A good-length delivery on off. Rassie van der Dussen is solid in his front foot defence. A maiden over by Wagner.
Back of a length, on off. Bavuma blocks it out.
That's a nice punch off the back foot by Bavuma! Back of a length, around off. Bavuma punches it through covers and gets three runs as the fielder cuts it off.
A length delivery on off. Rassie van der Dussen blocks it out.
A short ball, on off. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
Back of a length, around off. Bavuma goes back and punches this to cover-point.
Bouncer to finish the over! He bangs this short on middle but Bavuma ducks under it rather comfortably.

An overthrow and they get a run in the end. A full ball, outside off. Rassie van der Dussen prods and pushes it towards cover. Tim Southee there, collects the ball and has a shy at the striker's end but he misses.
On a length, angling across the batter. Temba Bavuma leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, around off. Temba Bavuma defends it onto the deck.
FOUR! Edgy but Bavuma had slashed hard at it! Back of a length, outside off. Temba Bavuma throws the kitchen sink at it and it goes off the thick outside edge over the slip cordon for a boundary.
A length ball, angling across the batter. Temba Bavuma lets it through to the keeper.
A full ball, on middle. Temba Bavuma leans and pushes it towards cover but not in the gap.
Southee serves a length ball, around off. Rassie van der Dussen gets forward and blocks it.
A bit full and outside off. Rassie van der Dussen lunges forward and defends it.
A full ball, on offf; Rassie van der Dussen skips down the track and eases it to mid on.
On a length, way outside off. Rassie van der Dussen leaves it alone.
Back of a length, around off. Rassie van der Dussen stands tall and blocks it to the off side.
A full ball, well outside off. Rassie van der Dussen lets it be. A maiden over from Southee!
Jamieson starts his spell with a length ball, outside off. Temba Bavuma lets it sail through to the keeper.
A well-directed bumper, around off. Temba Bavuma hangs back to keep it out but it hits the splice and luckily for Bavuma, the ball lands in front of the gully fielder.
A length ball, on off. Temba Bavuma defends it to the off side.
Pitches it up, around off. Temba Bavuma blocks it back to the bowler.
Good-length delivery, jagging back in from middle. Temba Bavuma tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Back of a length, around off. Temba Bavuma keeps it out. Back-to-back maiden overs from the Kiwi bowlers.
On a length, around off. Rassie van der Dussen blocks it to the off side.
FOUR! UP AND OVER! A full ball, outside off. Rassie van der Dussen looks for a drive and it goes off the outer half of the blade over the cover-point fielder for a boundary.

NOT OUT! Rassie van der Dussen escapes! Good review from him! Wagner bends his back and serves a short ball, around leg. Rassie van der Dussen shuffles across and looks to pull but he misses. New Zealand appeals and the umpire raises his finger. Rassie van der Dussen reviews it straightaway and the UltraEdge shows that there is no bat involved, as there is no spike on it.
FOUR! Top shot! A full ball, outside off. Rassie van der Dussen prods and carves it through cover-point for a boundary.
A length ball, on middle. Rassie van der Dussen tucks it around the corner and takes a single.
A good-length delivery, outside off and angling across the batter. Temba Bavuma leaves it alone.
Short of a length, outside off. Rassie van der Dussen lets it through to the keeper.

Jamieson goes full, outside off. Rassie van der Dussen presses forward and drives it a bit uppishly through the mid off region. The fielder there gets a hand to it but the ball goes past him. The batters take three runs.
On a length, angling in from off. Temba Bavuma covers the line of the ball and nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Good-length delivery, around off. Temba Bavuma blocks it off the front foot.
This is a length ball, just outside off that takes off from a length. Bavuma does well to keep it out with soft hands.
Back of a length, outside off. Temba Bavuma leaves it alone watchfully.
Back of a length, around middle. Rassie van der Dussen stays back and turns it towards mid-wicket.
A short ball, around leg. Rassie van der Dussen hangs back and pulls it along the ground towards fine leg for a single.
On a length ball, around off. Temba Bavuma blocks it off the front foot.
Nicely done! A full ball, around off. Temba Bavuma prods and drives it back past the bowler through mid off. The fielder there does well to cut it off and the batters take three runs.
Shorter in length, around leg. Rassie van der Dussen tucks it towards square leg.
A bumper way down leg. Rassie van der Dussen sways away from the line of the delivery.
Back of a length, outside off. Bavuma cuts it to cover-point.
A quick single this time! A length delivery on off. Bavuma pushes it towards mid on and sets off for a single. The fielder there has a shy at the bowler's end but misses and a single is completed.
Goes short on off. Rassie van der Dussen hangs on the back foot and pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
A fullish delivery on off. Bavuma drives it to mid off.
WIDE! This time he goes short again on middle but it is a bit too high and the umpire calls it wide.
Short delivery and around off. Bavuma just sways away from the line of the ball and lets it go.
Good delivery to end the over! In that channel around off this time. Bavuma leaves it alone.

FOUR! What a cracking shot this is! Short delivery around leg, the field is set for the short delivery. Rassie van der Dussen though, pulls it quite well and gets it in the gap towards backward square leg for a boundary.
Shorter delivery on middle again. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it to fine leg for a couple this time.
FOUR! He takes on the short ball again and hits this in the gap for a boundary. Short delivery, around leg. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it to backward square leg for a boundary.

Oh, dear! Colin de Grandhomme has dropped a sitter! Another short delivery on middle. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it again but this time straight to the square leg fielder. Colin de Grandhomme there, drops it and Neil Wagner is left frustrated.
Back of a length, around leg. Rassie van der Dussen works it to backward square leg for a couple.
Short ball again to end the over. It is around leg. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it to fine leg for a single. End of an eventful over from Wagner!
A good-length delivery, outside off. Rassie van der Dussen leaves it alone.
Back of  a length, on off. Rassie van der Dussen blocks it out.
A fuller delivery on middle. Rassie van der Dussen drives it to mid-wicket this time off the inner half of his blade.

FOUR LEG BYES! Kyle Jamieson drifts it down the leg side this time. Rassie van der Dussen looks to flick it but misses. The ball brushes his pads and goes towards the long leg fence for a boundary. There is an appeal from Kyle Jamieson but it was going down leg.
A short delivery, wider and outside off. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it from there and gets a single to deep square leg.
Back of a length, outside off. Bavuma punches it through covers for a couple. 100 comes up for South Africa! The lead is now 172!
Wagner continues with the short-pitch stuff. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it past square leg for a single.
A good-length delivery outside off and angling across. Bavuma leaves it alone.
Tad fuller this time outside off. Bavuma lets it go again.
Shorter length delivery on middle. Bavuma rides the bounce and works it behind square on the leg side for a single.
Short delivery on off. Rassie van der Dussen pulls it to square leg now.

OUT! CAUGHT AND BOWLED! The partnership is finally broken and it is that man again, Neil Wagner with his short-pitch stuff! A short delivery around off and slower in pace this time. Rassie van der Dussen is early in his pull this time as the ball holds onto the surface. He ends up just checking his shot and the ball loops up in the air towards the bowler. Neil Wagner dives forward and takes a fantastic catch. Wagner is pumped up and he provides his side with a glimmer of hope just when South Africa were taking the game away.
Howout: c & b Neil Wagner

Commentary: A length ball, outside off. Temba Bavuma leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Temba Bavuma shoulders his arms at it.
A length ball, on middle. Temba Bavuma nudges it around the corner and sets off for a quick run.
A full ball, around off. Kyle Verreynne prods and keeps it out.
Another ball, full and outside off. Kyle Verreynne drives but straight to the man at extra cover.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne stays back and punches it towards cover.
A bumper, angling across the batter. Temba Bavuma ducks underneath.
Back of a length, around off. Temba Bavuma hangs back and defends it solidly towards cover.
Wagner persists with short-pitched stuff, around leg. Temba Bavuma lets it through to the keeper.
On a length, outside off. Temba Bavuma mistimes his cut shot towards the cover fielder.
Short of a length, on off. Temba Bavuma gets right behind the line of the ball and defends it.
Another bumper, around middle and leg. Temba Bavuma pulls it uppishly but wide of the square leg fielder for a couple of runs.
On a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne lets it through to the keeper.
A short delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne pulls it to deep square leg for a couple.
Short of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it out.
A full ball, on middle. Kyle Verreynne drives it back past the bowler through mid on and takes a run as the mid on fielder cuts it off with a dive.
Short and wide, outside off. Temba Bavuma cuts it without much timing towards point.
Nicely played! Jamieson serves a full ball, on middle. Bavuma gets forward and drives it past the mid on fielder for a couple of runs.
A length ball, outside off and angling across the batter. Kyle Verreynne shoulders his arms at it.
Full and wide, outside off. Kyle Verreynne offers no shot to this one.
A full ball, angling across the batter from off. Kyle Verreynne lunges forward and defends it towards cover-point.
Good-length delivery, well outside off. Kyle Verreynne lets it sail through to the keeper.
Too full and wide, outside off. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone.
Another ball, full and around off. Kyle Verreynne prods and drives it without much timing wide of the mid off fielder for a single.
Back of a length, around middle. Kyle Verreynne stays back and tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Good-length delivery, around off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it off the front foot.
Henry goes full and on middle. Kyle Verreynne drives it back to the bowler. Henry sticks his right hand out and stops it. No run there.
A length ball, well outside off. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone.
BEAUTY! A length ball, around that corridor of uncertainty. Kyle Verreynne stays back to defend but the ball jags away a bit to beat his outside edge.
A full ball this time, on off. Kyle Verreynne prods and pushes it through the mid on region for a brace.
Good-length ball, angling across the batter. Temba Bavuma leaves it alone.

OUT! CAUGHT! Neil Wagner does the trick yet again! You just can't keep this man out of the contest! He runs in for his team every single day and provides the breakthrough when his team needs it the most! This was a full ball, outside off, enticing the batter to drive. Bavuma prods and looks for a booming drive but it goes off the splice of the blade, straight to Tim Southee at cover who takes a sharp catch. New Zealand get rid of the set batter. GAME ON!
Howout: c Tim Southee b Neil Wagner

Commentary: Wagner welcomes Mulder with a bouncer! A short delivery on middle. Mulder ducks under it.
Back of a length, on off. Wiaan Mulder taps it to the off side.
On a length, around off. Wiaan Mulder stays back, covers the line of the ball and defends it onto the deck.
Another short ball to end the over. On off this time. Mulder sways away from the line of the ball.
A length delivery outside off. Kyle Verreynne punches it to covers.
A good-length delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne lets it go.
On a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne pushes it towards the off side.
FOUR! Nice shot! Short and a bit of width provided this time. Kyle Verreynne cuts it through point for a boundary.
Full ball and angling into middle. Kyle Verreynne clips it to mid-wicket.
A fuller delivery on middle again. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid on this time.
Wagner serves this on a length, on off. Mulder blocks this off the back foot.
Goes fuller on off. Mulder defends it off the outside half of his blde to backward point.
Another full ball, quite suprisingly by Wagner. It is outside off and Mulder leaves it alone.
Here we go...a short ball on off this time. Mulder pulls it to fine leg for a single.
On a length, on middle. Kyle Verreynne pushes it towards the leg side.
On a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it towards the off side.
Back of a length, on off. Mulder blocks it out.
Back of a length, on middle. Mulder pushes it to mid on.
On a length, on middle. Mulder works it right of square leg for a single.
This is fuller on middle. Kyle Verreynne works it right of mid on for a single.
Pulls his length back again, on off. Mulder punches it to mid off and Colin de Grandhomme collects the ball and shines the ball for his bowler.
Shorter delivery on off. Mulder pulls it past square leg and gets a couple this time.
Fullish delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to cover-point. Will Young stops it.
A length delivery angling across the batter. Kyle Verreynne lets it go now.
A length delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne gets well forward and blocks it towards the off side.
Pulls his length back this time on middle. Kyle Verreynne works it towards the leg side.
Slightly shorter and outside off. Kyle Verreynne punches it through covers for a couple.
A length delivery, outside off and angling across the batter. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone.
A good-length delivery around off. Mulder defends it towards the off side.
Slightly shorter outside off. Mulder punches it to covers now.
Back of a length, on off. Mulder blocks it out solidly.
An appeal from Matt Henry but a big inside edge there! A length delivery on off. Mulder looks to defend but gets the inside edge onto his pads.
A length delivery on middle. Mulder works it towards the leg side.
Goes fuller this time on middle. Mulder nudges it towards the leg side.
Southee starts with a good-length delivery, around off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it out.
Full and outside off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to the man at cover-point.
On a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne leans and blocks it out solidly.
Short of a length, around middle. Kyle Verreynne keeps it out on the leg side.
An overpitched ball, outside off. Kyle Verreynne looks to drive but toe-ends it towards the extra cover fielder.
A full ball, outside off. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone.
Back of a length, around off. Wiaan Mulder stands tall and defends it to the off side.
A bit fuller this time, on off. Wiaan Mulder gets forward and blocks it.
Drags his length back and serves a length ball, on the pads. Wiaan Mulder nudges it around the corner and hands the strike back to Kyle Verreynne.
Good-length ball, around leg. Kyle Verreynne tucks it towards fine leg and takes a run.
Back of a length, outside off. Wiaan Mulder lets it through to the keeper.
A short ball, on middle. Wiaan Mulder swivels and pulls it along the ground towards fine leg for a single.
Back of a length, outside off. Wiaan Mulder looks to cut but ends up mistiming it towards the point fielder.
Good-length delivery, around off. Wiaan Mulder presses forward to block it.
Fuller in length, around off. Wiaan Mulder gets behind the line of the ball and defends it solidly.
Southee bangs it into the deck, outside off. Wiaan Mulder pulls it along the ground towards mid-wicket.
Full and wide, outside off. Wiaan Mulder lets it through to the keeper.
On a length, around off. Wiaan Mulder keeps it out. A maiden over from Southee!
A length ball, around middle. Kyle Verreynne clips it to the leg side for a single. The lead is now 200!
A full ball, angling down leg. Wiaan Mulder misses his flick.
Good-length delivery, on leg. Wiaan Mulder nudges it to the leg side for a run.
This is darted on the pads. Kyle Verreynne tucks it towards square leg.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne hangs back to block it out.
Short of a length, around middle. Kyle Verreynne sits back in his crease and punches it towards mid on.
Southee serves it on a length, on middle. Wiaan Mulder keeps it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Wiaan Mulder stands tall and punches it towards the cover fielder.
Pitches it up, around off. Mulder gets forward and defends it.
A low full toss, angling back in sharply. Wiaan Mulder manages to get his bat down in time and keeps it out.
A short ball, angling down leg. Wiaan Mulder pulls it behind square on the leg side for a run.
On a length, around middle. Kyle Verreynne hangs back and tucks it towards mid-wicket.
A length ball, around leg. Wiaan Mulder tickles it to fine leg and takes a single.
Short of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne gets on top of the bounce and punches it through the point region for a couple of runs.
A length ball, angling down leg. Kyle Verreynne misses his flick yet again.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Kyle Verreynne defends it on the leg side.
Short of a length, angling in from middle. Kyle Verreynne turns it towards mid-wicket.

FOUR! Nicely done! A welcome boundary for South Africa! Slightly shorter in length and outside off. Kyle Verreynne stays back, opens the bat face and caresses it through the backward point region for a boundary.
On a length, around middle. Wiaan Mulder gets behind the line of the ball and blocks it.
A full ball, outside off. Wiaan Mulder drives but straight to the mid off fielder.
Good-length delivery, around off. Wiaan Mulder gets forward and defends it solidly.
A short ball, outside off. Wiaan Mulder looks to pull but is way too early in his shot. It goes off the bottom half of the blade towards deep square leg for a single.
On a length and outside off. Kyle Verreynne lets it through to the keeper.
A rare full toss, outside off. Kyle Verreynne drives it without much timing wide of mid off and takes a run.
Good-length ball, on off. Kyle Verreynne prods and pushes it towards cover.
A full ball, outside off. Kyle Verreynne lunges forward and drives it to the man at extra cover.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne stays back and taps it to the off side.
Short of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne hops in his crease and punches it towards the extra cover fielder.
Pitches it up, around off. Kyle Verreynne prods and blocks it out.
Shorter in length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne rocks back and cuts it towards point but not in the gap. A maiden over from Colin de Grandhomme! That will be STUMPS on Day 3!
Confident shot straightaway by Mulder! Back of a length,outside off. Mulder cuts it firmly to point.
Back of a length again, around off. Mulder punches this off the back foot to covers.
Goes fuller this time on middle. Mulder works it to mid-wicket this time.
Pulls his length back again and serves this on off pole. Mulder punches it back to the bowler.
On a length, on middle. Mulder works it right of square leg for the first run of the morning.
A good-length delivery, around off. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone. Just a one fullish delivery in the first over by Southee.
On a length, on middle. Mulder works it to short mid-wicket.
Another delivery, on a length, on off. Mulder blocks it out.
Slightly short of a good length this time, on off. Mulder with a solid block again.
This time a fuller delivery on off. Mulder drives it to mid off.
On a length, on off. Mulder blocks this solidly from his crease.
Slightly fuller this time around off. Mulder defends this off the front foot.
A good-length delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne leaves it out.
On a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it on up this time and towards cover-point.
Goes fuller this time on off at 127.9 kph. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid off.
Short and a bit of width provided this time. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to gully this time.
A good-length delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to silly mid off this time.
Another fullish delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it back to the bowler.
A low full toss this time on off at 134.8 kph. Mulder drives it back to the bowler.
On a length, on middle. Mulder pushes it towards the leg side.
A good-length delivery on off this time. Mulder comes forward and blocks it.
Slighly short this time on off. Mulder pulls it to short mid-wicket.
This time a bit more short on middle. Mulder pulls it nicely to backward square leg for a single.
On a good length, on off. Kyle Verreynne is right forward to block it. Another good over by Henry. A sedate start by South Africa this. Just two runs so far in the four overs bowled this morning.
On a length, on middle. Mulder works it to short mid-wicket.
On a length, around off at 127.8 kph. Mulder defends this off the outside half of his blade to backward point.
Back of a length, on off. Mulder punches it towards the leg side.
A full delivery on leg. Mulder flicks it to deep square leg for a single.
Again a full delivery on middle and leg. Kyle Verreynne glances it to fine leg for a single.
Short delivery on off. Mulder pulls it to fine leg for a single.
Goes fuller on off. Mulder drives it to mid on now.
On a length, on off. Mulder blocks it out this time.
Another full delivery on off. Mulder drives it to mid off.
Back of a length, on middle. Mulder works it towards backward square leg for a couple.
Good short delivery this time, around off. Mulder sways away from the line of the ball.

FOUR! Another short ball and this time it produces a first boundary of the day. A shorter delivery on middle and leg. Mulder pulls it but gets a top edge the fall flies off towards long leg fence for a boundary.
A length delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to sweeper cover for a single.
A length delivery on off. Mulder punches it towards the off side.
Back of a length, on middle. Mulder punches it to mid on.
FOUR! Finds the gap this time! A fuller delivery on off. Mulder drives it crisply through covers and Kyle Jamieson runs behind it from mid off but fails to stop it. A boundary for Mulder.
A good-length delivery, outside off. Mulder leaves it alone this time.
Ohh...that's a tight leave! On a good-length and this time, around off. Mulder leaves it again the ball just shapes into him a little this time and goes past just away from the off pole.
On a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it out onto the turf.
A shorter delivery on off this time. Kyle Verreynne looks to pull but misses. The ball hits his shoulders.
A length delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne pushes it to short cover.
FOUR! Nicely played! On a length, around leg. Kyle Verreynne tucks it fine towards long leg fence for a boundary.
A good-length delivery around off. Kyle Verreynne pushes it towards the off side.
A short delivery on off to end the over. Kyle Verreynne pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
FOUR! Fifty partnership up and this has been a handy little partnership for South Africa. A shorter delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne pulls it in front of square for a boundary.
A fullish delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to deep extra-cover for a couple. Southee went 'round the wicket this time.
A fullish delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid off.
On middle and fuller. Kyle Verreynne flicks it through mid-wicket this time. Wagner runs behind it from mid on and the batters run three. Good work by Wagner to stop this near the fence with a slide.
A good-length delivery around off. Mulder lets it go.
Another good-length delivery going across Mulder and he leaves it alone again.
FOUR! Short balls are not working here for New Zealand! A shorter length delivery around leg. Nice height for Kyle Verreynne to pull and he pulls it to backward square leg for a boundary.
Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne punches it to cover-point.
On a length and around off. Kyle Verreynne just opens the face of his blade and the ball goes through backward point region. The batters run three.
On a length, on off. Mulder blocks it out.
A short delivery on off. Mulder pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
Another delivery on the shorter side on middle. Kyle Verreynne pulls this in front of square the fielder in the deep runs to his left and cuts if off. Two runs taken.
FOUR! Wagner is greeted with a boundary here! Back of a length, outside off. Mulder cuts it through point for a boundary.
A good-length delivery, outside off and angling across. Mulder lets it go.
Back of  a length, outside off. Mulder leaves it alone.
On a length, around off and angling across. Mulder defends this to backward point.
Ohh..finds his length this time. In that channel around off and angling across Mulder. He presses forward to defend this but the ball beats the outside edge of his blade.
A length delivery, outside off. Mulder lets it go comfortbably this time.
Short and wide outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to cover-point this time.
On a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it out.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne goes back and punches it to mid off.
On a length, on middle at 127.9 kph. Kyle Verreynne pushes it to mid on.
Hits that length hard again at 132.9 kph, on off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it out. Some extra bounce this time for Kyle Jamieson.
On the shorter side, around off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to gully this time.
On a length and angling across outside off. Mulder leaves it alone.
Back of a length, outside off. Mulder punches it to deep point for a single.
On a length and angling across the right-hander. Kyle Verreynne pushes it to point.
On a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne gets right forward and blocks it towards cover-point.
Goes fuller on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid off this time.
A length delivery, this time on middle and Kyle Verreynne blocks it onto the turf.
Goes full on middle. Mulder flicks it to deep square leg for a single.
Another fullish delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid off this time.
This time a bit of shape into the batter. Kyle Verreynne drives this off the inside half of his blade to backward square leg for a single.
FOUR! Well played by Mulder! Back of a length, around leg. Mulder just paddle this fine towards the long leg fence. Wagner comes running in from fine leg and puts in a dive but fails to stop it.
On a length, on off. Mulder knocks it onto the turf.
NO BALL! On a length, on middle. Mulder blocks it towards the leg side. Kyle Jamieson oversteps and he has to charge in again to bowl the last ball off the over.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Ohh...the extra ball has done the trick! This was not in the plan but Kyle Jamieson gets rid of well-set Mulder and breaks this dangerous partnership. A perfect delivery this by Kyle Jamieson. On a good length and around off. Mulder presses forward to defend it but the ball straightens after pitching and it catches the outisde edge of his blade. The ball goes towards right of Tom Blundell behind the stumps and Tom Blundell dives full length to take a one-handed stunner. A breakthrough for South Africa when the game was just drifting away from them.
Howout: c Tom Blundell b Kyle Jamieson

Commentary: Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne hangs back and cuts it to deep point for a single.
A short ball, on middle. Marco Jansen ducks underneath.
A length ball, around middle. Marco Jansen defends it out.
Back of a length, around off. Marco Jansen prods and keeps it out.
Another delivery, on a length, around off. Jansen gets forward and blocks it.
Hits the deck hard, around off. Marco Jansen covers the line of the ball and defends it out.
A length ball, angling in from middle. Kyle Verreynne tickles it to fine leg and brings up his FIFTY with a single. A good innings so far from South Africa's wicketkeeper.
Bangs it into the deck, outside off. Marco Jansen sways away from the line of the ball.
Back of a length, on off. Marco Jansen keeps it out.
BEATEN! A length ball, just outside off and shaping away a bit. Marco Jansen feels for it but the ball beats his outside edge.
Good-length ball, outside off. Marco Jansen lets it be.
Short of a length, just outside off. Marco Jansen gets low and lets it sail through to the keeper.
Driven hard but straight to the fielder. Full and outside off. Kyle Verreynne drives but finds the fielder at extra cover.
On a length and angling across the batter. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone.
Wagner serves it on a length, well outside off. Kyle Verreynne shoulders his arms at it.
On a length, around off and angling across the batter. Kyle Verreynne keeps it out.
Good-length delivery, around off. Kyle Verreynne gets solid in his front foot defence.
Back of a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne gets forward and defends it. A maiden over from Neil Wagner.
On a length, around off. Marco Jansen gets behind the line of the ball to block it.
Back of a length, outside off. Marco Jansen punches it through covers for a brace.
Slightly fuller and on off. Marco Jansen pushes it towrads cover.
A bumper, around off. Marco Jansen ducks underneath.
On a good-length, around off. Marco Jansen blocks it out.
Jamieson serves a short ball, aroud off. Marco Jansen lets it through to the keeper.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne stays back and taps it to point.
FOUR! Width on offer and Kyle Verreynne pounces on it! Short of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it past point and bags a boundary.

DROPPED AND FOUR! Tom Blundell drops one now! Another ball, short and wide, outside off. Kyle Jamieson throws his bat at it. The ball catches the outside edge and flies just past the diving keeper for a boundary.
Around off, blocked out.
Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne does not offer a shot to this one.
Good-length ball, around off. Kyle Verreynne hangs back to block it.
Short of a length, well outside off. Marco Jansen does not bother playing at it. Kyle Jamieson oversteps again and the umpire signals no ball.
Hits the length hard, around off. Marco Jansen blocks it solidly.
Good-length delivery, around off. Marco Jansen rocks back to keep it out.
BEATEN ALL ENDS UP! A length ball, just outside off that jags back in late. Marco Jansen looks to defend but the ball sneaks through his bat and pad.
A length ball, around off. Marco Jansen blocks it.
Fuller in length, outside off. Marco Jansen pushes it towards cover.
Jamieson drags his length back, around off. Marco Jansen defends it solidly.
A full ball, around middle. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid on,
Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone.
Shorter in length and angling across the batter. Kyle Verreynne guides it to deep point and rotates the strike.
BEATEN! A good-length ball, landing around off that shapes away a bit. Marco Jansen looks to defend but the ball beats his outside edge.
A length ball, on off. Marco Jansen defends it off the front foot.
Back of a length, well outside off. Marco Jansen lets it through to the keeper.
Colin de Grandhomme starts wth a full ball, on off. Kyle Verreynne pushes back to the bowler.
On a length, outside off. Kyle Jamieson cuts it through point for a single.
A yorker-length ball, on off. Marco Jansen digs it out.
Full and outside off. Marco Jansen drives it to the man at extra cover.
Short of a length, around off. Marco Jansen lets it be.
A full ball, on middle. Marco Jansen leans and drives it to mid on.
On a length and angling across the batter. Kyle Verreynne blocks it.
Fuller in length, on the pads. Kyle Verreynne flicks it through mid-wicket and bags a couple of runs.
This one is on a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne defends it.
On a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne stays back to defend.
A full ball, outside off. Kyle Verreynne drives but finds the fielder ar extra cover.
Back of a length, on middle. Kyle Verreynne stands tall and blocks it.
Pitches it up, on off. Marco Jansen blocks it off the front foot.
Edged but safe! A full ball, outside off. Marco Jansen looks for a booming drive but he gets an outside edge which falls short of the gully fielder.

NOT OUT! Colin de Grandhomme drags his length back, outside off. Marco Jansen looks to cut but he misses. Colin de Grandhomme feels that there was a tickle on it and he convinces his skipper to take a review. The UltraEdge shows that there was no bat involved and New Zealand lose a review.
FOUR! Boundary now for Jansen! Colin de Grandhomme drifts on the pads this time. Jansen flicks it towards backward square leg for a boundary.
On middle and fuller. Jansen works it to mid-wicket for a single.
Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne stays back and punches it through the point region to collect a single.
A very full delivery outside off. Kyle Verreynne carves it to deep point for a single.
A length delivery, on off. Jansen drives it to mid off.
Beaten this time! A good-length delivery and angling across the right-hander. Jansen looks to drive but misses.
On a length and around off. Jansen pushes it to deep point for a single.
A length delivery on middle and 123.5 kph. Kyle Verreynne works it to mid-wicket for a single.
Another delivery, on a length and around leg. Jansen works it towards backward square leg for a single.
A length delivery on off. Jansen drives it back to the bowler.

OUT! TAKEN! Ohh...what a catch! Will Young, you beauty! Produces a moment of brilliance to lift his team here! Absolutely fabulous stuff. A length delivery on middle. Jansen flicks this aerially towards deep mid-wicket. Young runs to his left and the ball is travelling away from him and it's even behind him. He, however, dives to his left and takes a one-handed stunner to ger rid of Jansen. His team-mates are thrilled and Marco Jansen is absolutely stunned after seeing that effort from Young. So two great ctaches from Kiwis this morning.
Howout: c Will Young b Colin de Grandhomme

Commentary: This time, Colin de Grandhomme produces a peach! A good-length delivery around off. Rabada goes pushing for it but the ball seams away a bit and beats the outside edge of his blade.
A length delivery, outside off. Rabada leaves it alone.
This time fullish length, outside off. Rabada lets it go again.
This one again, shapes away from Rabada. He leaves it alone.
FOUR! EDGY! Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne stays back and throws his bat at it. It takes the outside edge and flies past the second slip fielder for a boundary.
FOUR! Boundary again. It has been a very good innings from Kyle Verreynne! A length delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it through backward point for a boundary.
A full toss this time and a bit high. It's a knuckle ball and Kyle Verreynne pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
On a length, on off. Rabada blocks it out.

The lead is now 301! A length delivery around off. Rabada pushes forward to defend but the ball catches the outside edge of his blade and races towards the third man fence. The fielder cuts it off and the batters run couple.
A fuller delivery on middle. Rabada works it to mid on now.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne looks to cut but gets the inside half of his blade onto the turf.
Back of a length again, around off. Kyle Verreynne just chops it towards gully this time.
Back of a length, again. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to right of gully now.
Finally he goes fuller on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it through cover-point for a couple.
This one nips back in sharply. Kyle Verreynne looks to defend this length delivery on off. He, however, gets the inside edge onto his pads.

NOT OUT! Another one that jags back in sharply. A good-length delivery that is pitching around off. Kyle Verreynne looks to defend but the ball nips back in and hits his pads. There is a huge appeal but the umpire is not interested. New Zealand decide to take the review! The replays roll in and the UltraEdge shows no bat involved. The Ball Tracker rolls and it shows that it is pitching outside off and the ball is missing the stumps as it is going over them. So New Zealand lose their review and the original decision stays. Kyle Verreynne will continue after Lunch. New Zealand are 232/7 at Lunch on Day 4.
On a length and this first ball after Lunch comes back sharply into Rabada. He looks to defend but the ball hits him high on the pads.
FOUR! Lovely shot by Rabada! A fullish delivery on off and shaping into Rabada again. He drives this off the front foot past mid on for a boundary.
A length delivery on off. Rabada drives it crisply to short cover this time.
A fullish delivery on off. Rabada drives it to mid off now.
This time Southee beats him! A good-length delivery around off. Rabada tries to drive it but the ball beats the outside edge of his blade.
Beaten again! A fuller delivery outside off and shaping away. Rabada drives again away from his body and gets beaten.
A fuller delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid on.
Almost a yorker this time, a low full toss in the end on middle. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid on.
A length delivery on middle. Kyle Verreynne blocks it out.
Goes full on middle and a hint of inswing again. Kyle Verreynne drives it inside half of his blade to mid on for a single.
Nice shot but timing not perfect there. A length delivery on off. Rabada drives it over mid on off the inside half of his blade for a couple.
This time over mid off. A length delivery on off. Rabada lifts this over mid off. It goes high in the air but falls away from the fielder running to catch it from the ring and gets another couple.
Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne punches it through covers for a couple.
A fuller delivery on middle. Kyle Verreynne flicks it to mid-wicket for a single.
A good-length delivery, outside off. Rabada goes pushing for it but gets beaten off the outside edge.
Another play and a miss! A good-length delivery, outside off. Rabada looks to drive but is beaten again.
FOUR! Rabada has come out with a mood to play some shots here. A length delivery on off. Rabada lifts this towards deep extra-cover for a boundary.
SIX! This time a maximum! A fuller delivery on middle. Rabada stays deep in his crease and tonks it over long on for a maximum.
On a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne dabs it to point for a single.
Fuller delivery and outside off. Rabada leaves it alone.
Goes full again, outside off. Rabada tires to drive it but misses.
Back of a length, on middle. Rabada makes room and blocks it.
SIX! Ohh..Rabada is hurting New Zealand here! He backs away again  and Henry goes little short on middle. Rabada slaps it over long on for a biggie.
FOUR! This time a pull shot and runs are flowing now! Henry bangs this short on middle. Rabada is not backing away and pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a boundary now.
On a length, around middle. Kyle Verreynne tucks it wide of mid on and takes a run.
Back of a length, around off. Kagiso Rabada hangs back and defends it with soft hands.
FOUR! STREAKY! 50-run partnership is up now between these two! A full ball, outside off. Rabada looks to slog but it goes off the outside edge through the slip cordon for a boundary.
A full ball, outside off. Kagiso Rabada has a wild swing at it but he misses.
SIX! BANG! Rabada is having some fun out there! A length ball, on middle. Kagiso Rabada whacks it over deep mid-wicket for a biggie.
SIX! AND AGAIN! Southee comes 'round the wicket and serves it on a length, around middle. Kagiso Rabada backs away and smashes it over long on to bag a maximum.
FOUR! Kyle Verreynne joins the party now! Short and wide, outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it over point and collects a boundary.
Short of a length, outsdie off. Kyle Verreynne hangs back and cuts it to deep point for a run.
Back of a length, on middle. Kagiso Rabada nudges it to the leg side and takes a single.
A length ball, angling in from off. Kyle Verreynne prods and tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Play and a miss! On a length and outside off. Kyle Verreynne stays back and looks to cut it late but he misses.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne keeps it out.
Jamieson comes 'round the wicket and serves a length ball, on off. Kagiso Rabada blocks it onto the deck.
Leg bye! A slower ball, on a length, outside off. Kagiso Rabada shuffles across and looks to whip it away but misses. He gets hit on his pad and the batters take a leg bye.
Full and on middle. Kyle Verreynne flicks it through mid-wicket and takes a couple of runs.
FOUR! Nicely done! Good-length ball, just outside off. Kyle Verreynne stays back and carves it through covers for a boundary. He moves into the 90s now!
Around off, blocked out.
A length ball, angling in from middle. Kyle Verreynne tickles it behind square on the leg side for a run.
A length ball, on off. Kyle Verreynne keeps it out.
Slightly shorter in length, on middle. Kyle Verreynne hops in his crease and blocks it.
Good-length ball, jagging back in from off. Kyle Verreynne gets an inside edge behind the stumps and he tries to block it. A single taken.
A length ball, on middle. Kagiso Rabada defends it out.

OUT! CAUGHT! Kagiso Rabada holes out! Henry bangs it into the deck, around off. Kagiso Rabada flat-bats it towards Colin de Grandhomme at long on who takes a simple catch. End of a brilliant innings from Rabada! He has taken his team to a very formidable position here!
Howout: c Colin de Grandhomme b Matt Henry

Commentary: FOUR! Maharaj gets off the mark with a boundary and a bit edgy this time. On a good length around off. Maharaj gets an outside edge as he looks to defend it and the ball goes through the gully region for a boundary.
A full delivery on middle. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid on.
On a length, on middle. Kyle Verreynne works it towards backward square leg for a couple.
Back of a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne punches it to covers.
A length delivery, on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it nicely to mid off.
Back of a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to deep point for a single.
A fullish delivery on off. Maharaj blocks it out. A bit of inswing there.

FOUR! Century for Kyle Verreynne! What a sensational knock this has been from the wicket-keeper batter. This innings can well prove out to be a difference between the two sides. He has taken his team to a commanding position now. Coming to the ball, it is on a length, on middle. Kyle Verreynne works it towards backward square leg for a boundary. Kyle Verreynne is pumped up and his team-mates are all standing in the dressing room applauding this fabulous effort.
Henry follows it up with a length ball, around off. Kyle Verreynne keeps it out.
Back of a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it onto the deck.
Short of a length, on off. Kyle Verreynne covers the line of the ball and blocks it.

Excellent effort from Kyle Jamieson in the deep! A short ball, on middle. Kyle Verreynne looks to pull but it goes off the top edge towards the fine leg region. Jamieson there, hops in front of the ropes, catches the ball but parries the ball back in play as the momentum was takinh him over the ropes. The batters take a single.
On a length, on off. Keshav Maharaj blocks this off the front foot.
FOUR! He is now taking on the bowling. A short delivery outside off. Kyle Verreynne pulls it towards long on. The ball goes high in the air towards long on, one bounce into the fence.
FOUR! Another short ball and another boundary! Kyle Jamieson bangs it short on middle. Kyle Verreynne pulls it firmly towards deep square leg for a boundary.
FOUR! Three in a row now! Back of  a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne slaps it towards deep exra-cover for a boundary.
On a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne dabs it towards point and takes a risky single.

OUT! TAKEN! Keshav Maharaj departs now in a bid to get more quick runs! Kyle Jamieson bangs this short again on middle. Maharaj looks to pull but is hurried on this pull shot. He gets the top edge and the ball goes towards mid-wicket and Colin de Grandhomme runs behind to take a good catch. So nine down but the damage has been done.
Howout: c Colin de Grandhomme b Kyle Jamieson

Commentary: SIX! What a shot this is! Short and around off. Kyle Verreynne backs away and slaps it over point for a maximum.
On a length, on off. Lutho Sipamla blocks it out.
Back of a length, around off. Lutho Sipamla punches it to point and takes a single. The lead is now 400!
Short and wide outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to deepish point for a single now.
Southee bangs this short on middle and leg. Lutho Sipamla ducks under it.
A full delivery on middle. Lutho Sipamla flicks it through mid-wicket for a couple.
A very full delivery on off. Lutho Sipamla blocks it out.
A full delivery, outside off. Kyle Verreynne leaves this one alone.
A full delivery, on off. Kyle Verreynne drives it to deep cover and denies a single.
A length ball, on off. Kyle Verreynne blocks it out.
Back of a length, on middle. Kyle Verreynne defends it again.
WIDE! Full and very wide outside off. Kyle Verreynne leaves it alone and the umpire calls it wide.
A length delivery, again very wide outside off. Kyle Verreynne lets it go again but the umpire does not call it wide this time.
A full toss, outside off. Kyle Verreynne toe-ends this slap towards the off side.
On a length, around off. Lutho Sipamla pushes it towards the off side.
DROPPED! Kyle Jamieson drops a sitter now! A short delivery around leg. Lutho Sipamla pulls it straight to Kyle Jamieson at fine leg but he drops it. A single taken.
A fuller delivery on middle. Kyle Verreynne drives it to mid on for a single.
On a length, on off. Lutho Sipamla blocks it out.
Back of a length, on off. Lutho Sipamla blocks it out.
Short delivery this time on middle. Lutho Sipamla ducks under it.
Wide! Too short, outside off. Kyle Verreynne lets it be and the umpire calls it wide for height.
FOUR! Nicely done! Back of a length, on middle and leg. Kyle Verreynne swivels and pulls it behind square on the leg side for a boundary.
Banged into the deck, on middle. Kyle Verreynne pulls it along the ground towards deep square leg for a run.

FOUR! Cries of catch it but the ball goes over the keeper. Banged into the surface, around middle. Lutho Sipamla gets cramped and he looks to block. It goes the glove and flies over the keeper's head for a boundary.
On a length, around off. Lutho Sipamla keeps it out.
A short ball, outside off. Lutho Sipamla ducks underneath.
Back of a length, around off. Lutho Sipamla blocks it out.
A full ball, outside off. Kyle Verreynne drills it to long off for a run.

A misfield and they get the run in the end. Good-length ball, around off. Lutho Sipamla stays back to block but it goes off the outer half of the bat towards the gully region where the fielder fumbles and the batters take a single.
Back of a length, around off. Kyle Verreynne defends it off the back foot.
Short and wide, outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to deep point and settles for a single.
Good-length delivery, on off. Lutho Sipamla hangs back and punches it down to mid off.
Another ball, short of a length, on off. Lutho Sipamla blocks it out.
A slower ball, around leg. Kyle Verreynne steps out to flick but he misses.
Play and a miss! A slower ball, into the wicket, on middle. Kyle Verreynne shimmies down the track and looks to heave it away but he mises.
On a length, outside off. Kyle Verreynne cuts it to deep point and takes a single.
A short ball, on middle. Lutho Sipamla ducks underneath watchfully.
Wagner goes full, outside off. Lutho Sipamla drives but finds the cover fielder.
A short ball to end the over, down leg. Lutho Sipamla lets it sail through to the keeper.
Full and outside off. Kyle Verreynne drags it to deep point and manages only a single in the end.
A slower ball, full and around off. Lutho Sipamla digs it out.
A length ball, around middle. Lutho Sipamla tucks it to mid-wicket.
NASTY! A bumper, around off. Lutho Sipamla misses his pull and gets struck on his helmet.
Another short ball, around off. Lutho Sipamla tries to pull but it hits his forearm and then ricochets onto the helmet.
A full ball, outside off. Lutho Sipamla drags it towards mid on.
A slower ball, full and around leg. Kyle Verreynne clips it towards deep mid-wicket and comes back for the second run.
A yorker-length ball, on middle. Kyle Verreynne digs it out back to the bowler.
A full delivery on off. Kyle Verreynne digs it out to mid off for a single.
A short delivery on middle this time. Lutho Sipamla looks to pull but misses.
Another short delivery on middle. Lutho Sipamla ducks under it now. Not sure why South Africa are not declaring!

Here we go... South Africa declare now! A short delivery on middle. Lutho Sipamla pulls it to fine leg for a single. This has been a very good batting performance by South Africa. South Africa declare weith 354/9 in their second innings. New Zealand need 426 runs to win this Test match!
Good-length ball, around off. Tom Latham taps it to the off side and takes a single. New Zealand are underway!
Short of a length, outside off. Will Young leaves it alone.

OUT! CAUGHT! South Africa are off to a dream start! Rabada strikes in his first over and New Zealand lose a wicket early on. Rabada serves a full ball, outside off. Will Young looks for a booming drive but it takes the outside edge and goes straight to Temba Bavuma at gully who makes no mistake. Young departs for a duck and South Africa are on top! Not the kind of start that New Zealand would be hoping for!
Howout: c Temba Bavuma b Kagiso Rabada

Commentary: A short ball, angling down leg. Devon Conway leaves it alone.
FOUR! EDGY! Good-length ball, around off. Devon Conway looks to block but it goes off the outside edge past the slip fielder and into the fence.
A length ball, angling in from middle. Devon Conway clips it behind square on the leg side and takes a run.
A length ball, angling down leg. Devon Conway misses his flick.
BEATEN! On a length, just outside off. Conway has a poke at it but the ball beats his outside edge.
Back of a length, around off. Conway blocks it.
On a length and angling across the batter. Devon Conway lets it through to the keeper.
A good-length delivery, outside off. Conway leaves it alone.
Another length delivery, outside off. Conway leaves it again.

OUT! TAKEN! Rabada strikes again and sends back the Kiwi skipper! Rabada goes back of a length, on middle, angling into the body. Latham just tries to work it away towards the leg side but ends up hitting it towards the short leg fielder and Rassie van der Dussen there takes a sharp catch. Big wicket this and Kiwis are in early trouble here. Henry Nicholls is the next man in.
Howout: c Rassie van der Dussen b Kagiso Rabada

Commentary: A length ball, around middle. Henry Nicholls tucks it to the leg side for a run.
A length delivery, outside off. Conway lets it go.
Another good-length delivery angling across the left-hander and Conway lets it go.
A good-length delivery around off. Conway goes pushing for it but the ball beats the outside edge of his blade.
Back of a length, around middle. Devon Conway keeps it out.
Short of a length, down leg. Henry Nicholls sways away from the line of the ball.
Good-length delivery, just outside off. Henry Nicholls leaves it alone.
Another ball, on a length, just outside off and jagging back in late. Henry Nicholls lets it be and the ball goes just past the off pole.
Jansen bangs it into the deck, on middle. Henry Nicholls pulls it along the ground behind square on the leg side for a single.
On a length, around off. Devon Conway keeps it out.
Good-length delivery, otutside off. Devon Conway does not offer any shot to this one.
Back of a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls nudges it wide of mid-wicket for a run.

DROPPED! Back of a length, angling in from off and cramping the batter for room. Devon Conway looks to pull but he miscues it and the ball goes left of the backward square leg fielder. The fielder dives to his left and gets both hands on it but fails to pouch it.
Back of a length, around off. Devon Conway prods and blocks it.
Rabada hits the deck hard, around off. Devon Conway covers the line of the ball and defends it out.
Drop and run! On a length, outside off. Conway taps it to the off side and sets off for a quick run.
Good-length ball, around middle. Henry Nicholls looks to defend but it goes off the thick inside edge towards the short leg fielder.
Jansen serves a length ball, jagging back in from off. Devon Conway keeps it out.
Short of a length, outside off. Devon Conway leaves it alone.
Shorter in length, outside off. Devon Conway shuffles across a bit and helps it on its way towards deep square leg for a single.
On a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls works it towards mid-wicket and takes a quick single.
A bit full and on middle. Nicholls nudges it wide of mid-wicket and takes a single.
On a length, just outside off. Devon Conway lets it sail through to the keeper.
An appeal for LBW but turned down! A yorker-length ball, angling in from middle. Henry Nicholls fails to dig it out and gets hit on his pad. Might have gone down leg.
A length ball, around off. Henry Nicholls defends it out.
Good-length delivery, on middle. Henry Nicholls presses forward to block it.
A low full toss, on middle. Henry Nicholls drags it to mid on.
Short of a length, on off. Henry Nicholls keeps it out.
Rabada hits the deck hard, on middle. Henry Nicholls stays back and gets solid in his defence.
A bumper, around off. Devon Conway mistimes his pull towards the fine leg fielder on the bounce. A single taken.
Short and wide, outside off. Henry Nicholls looks to cut but it takes the underedge and lands into the deck.
Another ball that is short of a length, outside off. Henry Nicholls looks to cut hard but does not time it well.
On a length, around off. Henry Nicholls blocks it off the front foot.
Good-length ball, angling away from outside off. Henry Nicholls leaves it alone.
Jansen darts it on the pads. Henry Nicholls flicks it to deep square leg for one run.
A short ball, on off. Henry Nicholls ducks underneath.
Back of a length, around off. Henry Nicholls gets on top of the bounce and defends it.
Good-length ball, around off. Conway hangs back to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards the slip fielder, along the ground.
A length ball, jagging back in from middle. Henry Nicholls tucks it towards mid-wicket.
A bit fuller this time, on middle. Henry Nicholls prods and drives it to mid on.
Back of a length, around off. Henry Nicholls stands tall and blocks it out.
This is a length ball, around off that jags back in late. Devon Conway looks to defend but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards square leg.
Back of a length, angled down leg. Conway gets inside the line of the ball and leaves it alone.
A full ball, on middle. Devon Conway flicks it through the mid-wicket region. The batters take three runs.
On a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls works it towards mid-wicket and takes a quick single.
Short delivery on middle. Conway pulls it to deep square leg for a single.
Back of a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls nudges it towards the leg side.
A good-length delivery, on off and nipping into the batter. Conway defends this off the inside half of his blade towards mid-wicket for a single.
Shorter length and around leg. Henry Nicholls lets it go.
Back of a length, on middle. Henry Nicholls gets on the top of the bounce and nudges it towards the leg side for a single.
FOUR! A boundary this time! A full toss on the pads. Conway just flicks this off his pads towards the square leg fence for a boundary.
A good-length delivery, outside off and seaming away. Conway leaves it alone.
A fullish delivery on off. Conway drives it towards covers. Maharaj at short cover does well to stop it with a dive.
Shorter and turning away around off. Henry Nicholls pushes it towards the off side.

OUT! BOWLED! The spinner strikes on his second ball and New Zealand are in all sorts of trouble here! A slightly shorter delivery, around off. Henry Nicholls goes back to push it but completely misreads the turn here as the ball turns in sharply. The ball beats the inside edge of his blade and knocks over the middle pole. A big wicket this and Keshav Maharaj is showing his quality yet again.
Howout: b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: A fuller delivery on middle. Daryl Mitchell drives it to mid on for a single.
Slightly short on off. Conway goes back and pushes it towards mid on for a single.
Nicely tossed up on middle. Daryl Mitchell pushes it towards mid on.
Another loopy delivery on off. Daryl Mitchell gets forward and blocks it out.
Back of a length, on off. Conway defends it towards the leg side.
Goes fuller this time on off. Conway looks to drive it towards the off side but gets the inside half of his blade towards square leg.
On a length, on off. Conway again defends this off the inside half of his blade to square leg. A single this time.
Back of a length, around off at 133.8 kph. Daryl Mitchell blocks this off the back foot.
This time he gets fuller on off. Daryl Mitchell defends it towards the off side off the front foot now.
On a length, on middle. Daryl Mitchell blocks it out.
Tossed up around off. Conway gets well forward and defends it.
This time a bit shorter and turning into Conway. He goes back and pushes it towards backward point for a single.
SIX! Daryl Mitchell decides to take him on! A tossed up delivery on middle. Daryl Mitchell advances down the track and slams it down the ground for a biggie.
SIX! Another one, this is interesting from Daryl Mitchell! Tossed up again, around middle and leg. Daryl Mitchell skips down the track and tonks it over long on with ease.
Slower and on middle. Devon Conway gets well forward and blocks it.
Fuller on middle. Daryl Mitchell works it towards mid-wicket.
On a length, on off. Conway blocks this off the inside half of his blade towards the leg side.
On a length, on middle. Conway works it towards square leg.
A good-length delivery, outside off. Conway leaves it alone this time.
On a length, on off. Conway blocks it towards the off side.
On a length, around off. Conway blocks it out solidly yet again.
On a length, on off. Conway gets forward and blocks it out.
Tossed up, on middle. Daryl Mitchell blocks it off the front foot.
Flatter and quicker, on off. Daryl Mitchell defends it solidly.
Flatter ball, going on with the arm from middle. Daryl Mitchell nudges it through mid-wicket for a run.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Conway covers the line and keeps it out.
Slower through the air, just outside off and spinning in. Devon Conway looks to defend but it goes off the inside edge past the short leg fielder.
Floated, outside off. Devon Conway gets solid in his defence.
A full ball, on leg. Daryl Mitchell tickles it through the fine leg region for a brace.
Good-length delivery, around off. Daryl Mitchell defends it onto the deck.
Short of a length, around middle. Daryl Mitchell gets behind the line of the ball and dabs it onto the deck.
A yorker-length delivery, around off. Daryl Mitchell digs it out towards mid on.
BEATEN! Good-length delivery, around the corridor of uncertainty. Mitchell looks to defend away from his body but the ball zips past his outside edge.
A full ball, darted on the pads. Daryl Mitchell nudges it towards the mid-wicket fielder.
Tossed up, around off. Devon Conway blocks it off the front foot.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Devon Conway gets forward and blocks.
Floated, full and outside off. Devon Conway leaves it alone.

Nicely tossed up, around off and taking off from a length. Devon Conway looks to block it off the front foot but he gets an inside edge onto his thigh pad and luckily for him, the ball lands just in front of Dean Elgar at silly point.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Devon Conway drags it to long on for a single.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Daryl Mitchell gets forward and defends it.
Good-length delivery, around off. Devon Conway keeps it out.
On a length, around off. Devon Conway covers the line of the delivery and keeps it out.
On a length and angling in from off. Devon Conway defends it.
Good-length delivery, around off. Devon Conway prods and gets solid in his defence.
A full ball, on middle. Devon Conway flicks but the fielder at mid-wicket dives and stops the ball.
Sipamla serves a length ball, around off. Devon Conway blocks it off the front foot.
Tosses it up, around off. Daryl Mitchell prods and pushes it towards mid off.
Maharaj errs in line and spills it down leg. Mitchell lets it be.
Flatter ball, on middle. Daryl Mitchell keeps it out.
Floated, on a length, around middle. Daryl Mitchell prods and dabs it onto the deck with soft hands.
Flatter and quicker, on middle. Daryl Mitchell gets solid in his front foot defence.
Slower through the air, on a length, on middle. Daryl Mitchell gets forward and defends.
A full delivery on off. Conway defends it towards mid on.
FOUR! Conway with a good cover drive! This is overpitched, on off. Conway drives as his one hand comes off the handle. The ball goes through covers for a boundary.
On a length, on middle. Conway works it towards backward square leg.
Another length delivery on off. Conway blocks it out.
Back of a length, on off. Conway goes back and defends it comfortably.
On a length, around off. Conway is solid in his defence again. Not much happening off the deck or in the air but South Africa have been pretty disciplined with their lines and lengths so far.
Tossed up on middle and leg. Mitchell works it towards square leg.
Another loopy delivery on middle. Mitchell works it towards square leg and looks for a single but is sent back by his partner.
Tossed up around off. Mitchell blocks it out.
Slower in the air on middle. Mitchell blocks this off the front foot again.
Darted on middle and leg. Mitchell works it towards square leg.
Nicely tossed up on middle. Mitchell pushes it towards the leg side.
A full delivery on off. Conway pushes it towards the off side.
Goes fuller again and this time on middle. Conway works it left of mid on and gets a couple as the fielder cuts it off.
On a length, on middle. Conway gets forward and blocks it out.
FOUR! Good shot! This is fuller outside off. Conway leans forward and drives it through covers for a boundary.
FOUR! Jansen decides to bang this short but Conway is equal to the task and pulls it to deep square leg for a boundary. Conway is key here for New Zealand.
Fullish delivery, on off. Conway drives it to covers.
Tossed up on middle. Mitchell blocks it out.
Flatter and down the leg side. Mitchell lets it go.
Slower in the air on middle. Mitchell blocks this off the front foot.
Darted on leg this time. Mitchell works it towards square leg.
This is slower on middle with a hint of turn. Mitchell blocks this out.
A fuller delivery on off. Mitchell defends this off the front foot.
On a length, on off. Conway blocks it out.
On a length and this one jags back in a little. Conway defends this off the inside half of his blade towards the leg side.
On a length, on middle. Conway dabs it towards the leg side as his one hand comes off the handle.
Again his one hand comes off. A short delivery on off. Conway pulls this aerially but short of deep square leg for a single.
On a length, around off from 'round the wicket. Mitchell blocks it out.
Back of a length, on middle angling into the body. Mitchell blocks it towards mid on.
Tossed up, around off. Devon Conway drags it back to the bowler.
A loopy ball, well outside off. Devon Conway keeps it out.
Flatter and a bit quicker through the air, on middle. Devon Conway tucks it to the leg side.
Flatter and on a length, around middle. Devon Conway nudges it wide of mid-wicket and takes a single.
Flatter ball, on a length, on middle. Daryl Mitchell keeps it out.
Tosses it up, around off. Daryl Mitchell defends it off the front foot.
FOUR! TOP SHOT! A short ball, on middle. Conway gets on top of the bounce and pulls it in front of square to bag a boundary.
Back of a length, on middle. Conway blocks it off the front foot.
Good-length delivery, around off. Devon Conway keeps it out.
FOUR! BANG! A bumper, around off. Devon Conway stands tall and pulls it in front of square to fetch himself yet another boundary.
On a length, around middle. Devon Conway nudges it to the leg side for a single.
Leg bye! Back of a length, around leg. Daryl Mitchell looks to tuck it on the leg side but he misses and gets hit high on his body. The ball rolls to the leg side for a leg bye.
Tosses it up nicely, around off. Daryl Mitchell blocks it off the front foot.
On a length, around off. Daryl Mitchell covers the line of the ball to defend it.
Flatter ball, going on with the arm from off. Daryl Mitchell gets forward and keeps it out.
This is a flatter ball, on middle and going on with the angle. Daryl Mitchell looks to defend but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards square leg.
Floated, on a length, on middle. Daryl Mitchell keeps it out.
Slower through the air this time, on off. Daryl Mitchell presses forward and blocks it.
A stifled appeal for LBW but turned down! A length ball, around off. Conway looks to defend but he gets an inside edge onto his pad.
On a length, around off. Devon Conway blocks it out.
Good-length delivery, around off. Devon Conway plants his foot forward and defends it solidly.
Pitches it up, on middle. Conway lunges forward and blocks it.
Short of a length, on middle. Devon Conway rides the bounce nicely and dabs it in front of square on the leg side.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Devon Conway stays back and blocks it.
Floated, darted on the pads. Daryl Mitchell presses forward and tucks it towards square leg.
Tosses it up, around off. Daryl Mitchell keeps it out.

FOUR! Not the most convincing shot but Mitchell will take that! Mitchell skips down the track so Keshav Maharaj drags his length back, on middle. Mitchell looks for a slog but it goes off the inner half of the blade and over the mid-wicket fielder for a boundary. That brings up the 50-run stand between these two!
FOUR! Flatter ball, angling down leg. Daryl Mitchell tickles it past the leg slip fielder for another boundary.
Flatter and quicker, on off. Daryl Mitchell blocks it off the front foot.
Tosses it up, on middle. Daryl Mitchell gets forward and defends it out.
On a length, on off and coiming into Conway slightly. He blocks this off the front foot.
Back of a length, angling into middle this time. Conway pulls it to fine leg for a single.
Good delivery! On that good length, outside off. Daryl Mitchell leaves it alone. It comes back in slightly.
On a length with a nip back in, around off. Mitchell blocks it out.
Back of a length, on off. Mitchell rocks back and blocks it out.
Goes fuller this time on off at 129.9 kph. Mitchell defends this off the front foot. Oohhs and ahhs from the South African players!
A flatter delivery on off. Conway blocks it out.
Slower in the air on off. Conway gets forward and defends it towards the off side.
Tossed up on middle and leg. Conway works it towards the leg side.

Ohh... Conway almost played on there! Slightly shorter on a length, around off and turning into Conway. He goes back and blocks it onto the turf but the ball almost goes on to hit the stumps. Luckily for Conway, it goes just past the off stump.
On middle and turning into the batter. Conway works it towards the leg side.
Flatter on middle. Conway turns it towards square leg.
A full delivery on off. Mitchell drives it to mid off.
Back of a length, outside off. Mitchell punches it to covers.
Back of a length, on off. Mitchell blocks this off the back foot.
Drifting on the pads this time. Mitchell clips it to mid-wicket.
A length delivery on middle at 128.7 kph. Mitchell blocks this off the front foot.
Good tight line again. Back of a length, on off. Mitchell goes back and blocks it out.
Fuller delivery on off. Conway pushes it to long on for an easy single.
Flatter and quicker on off. Mitchell defends this off the front foot.
Nicely tossed up around off. Slower in pace. Mitchell reaches for it and drives it to covers.
On middle this time. Mitchell works it towards the leg side.
Quicker and flatter on middle and leg. Mitchell works it towards mid-wicket.
Bowls this slower on middle. Mitchell is well forward and blocks it.
On a length, on off. Conway blocks it out.
A length delivery on off. Conway defends it off his crease towards the leg side.
On a length, on middle at 128.9 kph. Conway clips it towards mid-wicket.
This has been a good spell from Lutho Sipamla. He has given away nothing to the batters to work with. On a length, on off. Conway just defends it onto the turf.
Back of a length, around off. Conway punches it towards covers.
Lutho Sipamla goes 'round the wicket and serves this on a length, outside off. Devon Conway lets it go.
Flatter ball, on middle. Daryl Mitchell stays back and keeps it out.

OUT! TIMBER! That is an absolute beauty from Maharaj to get rid of Mitchell! He has been troubling both Conway and Mitchell and finally gets his reward! Maharaj serves a flatter ball, on a length, on middle. Mitchell gets forward and looks to block but he misses as the ball spins away after landing and goes past his outside edge to shatter the off stump. The South African players are ecstatic and New Zealand are in deep, deep trouble now!
Howout: b Keshav Maharaj

Commentary: Quicker and fuller on off. Tom Blundell gets well forward and blocks it.
Darted on middle and leg. Tom Blundell works it towards the leg slip.
Nicely bowled again! Pulls his length back and it is on middle and turning away. Tom Blundell blocks it out off the front foot.
Another loopy delivery on off. Tom Blundell gets well forward again and defends it.
A full ball, on middle. Devon Conway tucks it towards mid-wicket.

Aerial but safe! A length ball, on middle. Conway stays back and looks to pull but it goes off the top edge just over the mid-wicket fielder for a brace. That brings up his FIFTY as well! A gritty knock from the southpaw so far!
FOUR! Glorious! A full ball, outside off. Devon Conway gets forward and carves it through the cover region for a boundary.
On a length, around middle. Devon Conway blocks it off the back foot.
Back of a length, just outside off. Devon Conway keeps it out.
A full ball, outside off. Devon Conway shoulders his arms to this one.
Tossed up, around off. Tom Blundell presses forward to block it.
A flatter ball, going on with the arm, from off. Tom Blundell hangs back and dabs it onto the deck in the end.
On a length, around off. Tom Blundell defends it off the front foot.
Slower through the air, around off. Tom Blundell gets solid in his front foot defence.
Tosses it up nicely, around off. Tom Blundell looks for a drive through covers but it goes off the inner half of the blade back to the bowler.
Floated, on a length, around off. Tom Blundell keeps it out.
A length ball, angling in from off. Devon Conway prods and tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Good-length delivery, around middle. Devon Conway stays back and blocks it.
Rabada hurls a wayward ball, down leg. Devon Conway lets it be. Kyle Verreynne behind the sticks does well to dive to his right and gather the ball.
On a length, jagging back in from middle. Conway tucks it around the corner and rotates the strike.
Good-length delivery, well outside off that nips back in late. Tom Blundell prods and leaves it alone.
A full ball, outside off. Tom Blundell offers no shot to that one.
Flatter ball, outside off and turning in sharply. Conway keeps it out off the back foot.
Tosses it up, around off. Devon Conway defends it off the front foot.
Looped up, on a length, outside off. Devon Conway presses forward to block.
Floated, on a length, around middle. Devon Conway keeps it out.
Slower through the air, way outside off. Conway smothers the spin and dabs it onto the deck.
Tossed up, on a length, outside off. Devon Conway prods to block but it goes off the outside edge past the slip fielder for a run.
A length ball, angling down leg. Devon Conway misses his flick.
Back of a length, around leg. Devon Conway just helps it on its way towards fine leg for a single.
Good-length ball, outside off. Tom Blundell leaves it alone for the keeper to collect.
Another ball, on a length, outside off and going on with the angle. Tom Blundell does not bother playing at that one.
Short of a length, around off. Tom Blundell hangs back and defends it onto the deck.
Back of a length, outside off. Tom Blundell defends it away from his body towards cover.
Tosses it up, around off. Devon Conway gets solid in his front foot defence.

DROPPED! A tough chance though! Floated, on a length, well outside off. Devon Conway plants his front foot forward and looks to block but it hits the splice and pops out straight to Dean Elgar at silly point who fails to grab the ball.
On a length, outside off. Devon Conway covers the line and blocks it.
Tossed up, outside off. Devon Conway drives it through cover and takes a couple of runs.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Conway punches it off the back foot through covers and takes a run.
Maharaj serves a flatter ball that goes on with the arm, from middle. Tom Blundell prods and tucks it to the leg side for a single. That will be STUMPS on Day 4!
Rabada starts with a length ball, outside off. Tom Blundell prods and leaves it alone.
A bit fuller this time, on middle. Tom Blundell leans and works it wide of mid on to rotate the strike. New Zealand are underway on Day 5!

A stifled appeal for caught behind but the umpire is not interested! Rabada comes 'round the wicket and serves a short ball, on middle. Devon Conway gets into an awkward tangle as he tries to duck underneath. The ball brushes his shoulder before going to the keeper.
On a length, outside off. Devon Conway leaves it alone.
FOUR! EDGY! Good-length delivery, around off. Devon Conway stays back and looks to block but it goes off the outside edge, past the second slip fielder for a boundary.
Full and wide, outside off. Conway does not bother playing at this one.
FOUR! Nicely done! Back of a length, outside off. Tom Blundell gets on top of the bounce and punches it behind square on the off side for a boundary.
A full ball, angling across the batter. Tom Blundell lets it be.
Jansen dishes out a short ball, around leg. Tom Blundell sways away from the line of the ball.
FOUR! Glorious! Fuller in length, outside off. Tom Blundell presses forward and carves it through the cover region to bag a boundary.
Jansen drags his length back, around middle. Tom Blundell blocks it back to the bowler.
Short of a length, just outside off. Tom Blundell lets it through to the keeper.
Good-length delivery, on off. Devon Conway gets solid in his front foot defence.
Slightly shorter in length, on middle. Devon Conway hangs back to keep it out.
On a length, outside off. Devon Conway prods and pushes it towards mid off.
A full ball, outside off. Devon Conway drives but finds the man at mid off.
A length ball, angling in from off. Devon Conway blocks it with soft hands.
Another ball, that comes on with the angle from off. Devon Conway covers the line of the ball to defend.
Back of a length, around off. Tom Blundell blocks it with ease.
On a length, around off. Tom Blundell hangs back to block.
Another delivery, on a length, around off. Blundell dabs it onto the deck.
A full ball, outside off. Tom Blundell shoulders his arms to this one.
Full and outside off, angling across the batter. Tom Blundell leaves it alone for the keeper to collect.
Back of a length, around leg. Tom Blundell rides the bounce nicely and just helps it on its way towards fine leg for a single.
A length ball, on off. Blundell blocks it off the front foot.
FOUR! Nicely played! A full ball, outside off. Tom Blundell presses forward and caresses it past the diving fielder at extra cover and mid off. The ball races away to the fence.
On a length, outside off. Tom Blundell lets it be.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Tom Blundell shoulders his arms at it.
Short of a length, on off. Tom Blundell gets behind the line of the ball and blocks it.
No ball! Short of a length, around off. Tom Blundell hangs back and defends it out. Rabada oversteps and the umpire signals a no ball.
Another ball, short and around off. Tom Blundell gets on top of the bounce and defends it towards cover.
Fuller in length, on off. Conway drives it to mid off.
Full again, attacking the stumps. Conway covers the line and drives it to mid on.
Length ball, outside off. Left alone.
On a length, outside off. Devon Conway lets it sail through.
On a good length, outside off, nipping away. Conway keeps it out.
Length, outside off. Conway leaves it alone. A maiden!
Good-length ball, outside off. Tom Blundell shoulders arms to that one.
On a length, on off. Tom Blundell defends it off the front foot.
On a length, in the fourth stump channel. Tom Blundell taps it to point.
Short ball, on off. Tom Blundell gets on top of the bounce and pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a run.
FOUR! Pulled away! Short ball again, this time to Conway, on middle. Devon Conway pulls it to deep square leg for a boundary.
Short ball yet again, on middle. Pulled to deep square leg for a single this time.
Length ball, around off. Devon Conway looks to defend. The ball goes off the inside edge past the stumps. The batters take a single.
FOUR! Easy pickings! Short of a length, on leg. Tom Blundell glances it to fine leg for a boundary.
Similar line and length, Tom Blundell glances it to deep square leg for a brace.
On a length, on leg. Tucked to deep square leg for a run.
Good-length ball, jagging back in, outside off. Devon Conway has a look and shoulders arms.
Outside off, an easy leave for Conway.
Mulder starts with a length ball, around off. Tom Blundell keeps it out.
This is full and outside off. Tom Blundell leaves it alone.
Fuller in length, well outside off. Tom Blundell lets it be.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Tom Blundell leaves it alone.
Back of a length, on middle. Tom Blundell nudges it around the corner and takes a single.
A length ball, jagging back in a bit from off. Devon Conway gets an inside edge and onto his pad.
Full and outside off. Tom Blundell lets it through to the keeper.
Back of a length, around off. Tom Blundell keeps it out.
Another ball, short and on off. Tom Blundell blocks it.
Back of a length, just outside off. Tom Blundell tries to cut but it goes off the inner half of the bat and onto the deck.
Full and outside off. Tom Blundell lets it be.
A length ball, darted on the pads. Tom Blundell flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.
Full and outside off. Tom Blundell does not offer any shot to that one.
On a length, around off. Tom Blundell keeps it out.
Fuller in length, outside off. Tom Blundell sways away from the line of the delivery.
Good-length ball, around off. Tom Blundell prods and blocks it to cover.
This is a full ball, well outside off. Tom Blundell leaves it alone.
Another ball, full and outside off. Tom Blundell shoulders his arms to it.
A length ball, jagging back in from off. Devon Conway presses forward and defends it.
Around off, blocked out.
Good-length delivery, around off. Conway defends it towards cover.
On a length and just outside off. Conway lunges forward and defends it.
A full ball, angling in from middle. Devon Conway tucks it towards fine leg for a single.
